{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2659690/extras/OECLASS_SCREEN2.png?t=1733425348\" />\u2e3b\u2e3b\u2e3b\u2e3b\u2e3b\u2e3b\u2e3b\u2e3b\u2e3b\u2e3b\u2e3b\u2e3b\u2e3b\u2e3b\u2e3b</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>\u25b6 OPERATION ATHENA FEATURES:</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Immersive and Impactful Gunplay</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Dynamic Leaning System</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Bold and Engaging AI</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Squad Specific Player Classes</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Elimination Game Mode (Terrorist Hunt)</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Hostage Rescue Game Mode</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Bomb Threat Game Mode</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Operations in Locations around the Globe</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><i>More Coming Soon!</i></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u2e3b\u2e3b\u2e3b\u2e3b\u2e3b\u2e3b\u2e3b\u2e3b\u2e3b\u2e3b\u2e3b\u2e3b\u2e3b\u2e3b\u2e3b</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2659690/extras/OEGIF_SOLOWIDE.gif?t=1733425348\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">\u25b6 Class system:</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> In Operation Athena you will play as one of four distinct operators. Each member is vital to mission success.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Team Leader:</h2> The Team Leader is an important member of the squad, the team leader designates roles, outlines mission plans and coordinates team movements.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Medic:</h2> The Medic is responsible for providing medical support to injured teammates and ensuring the squad's survivability during combat engagements. The Medic will utilize equi